            <h3><a name="rugby"></a>Old Mid-Whits RFC NatWest Rugby Force Day, Saturday 27th June</h3>
              <p>We have a big day coming up on Saturday 27th June which is our NatWest Rugby Force Day. We will be have some people up on Sanderstead High Street handing out <%= link_to "these flyers", "resource/OMWRFC_Leaflet.pdf" %> and will also have people up at the club carrying out various maintenance projects. If any members of the local community want to come up and lend a hand their help will be very much appreciated!</p>
          </div><!-- /col-md-10"> -->
          <div class-"col-md-2">
               <h3><%= link_to image_tag("http://images2.pitchero.com/club_logos/9625/1298890919.jpg", alt: "Old Mid Whits Rugby"), "http://www.omwrfc.co.uk" %></h3>
