            <h3><a name="organ"></a><%= link_to "Organ and Piano Recital", "/resource/brooks_concert.pdf"%>, Sunday 28th June 3pm</h3>
            <p>Recital to be held in All Saints' Church, Internationally famous organist Gerard Brooks and and his daughter Verity on the piano will perform music by Mozart, Debussy, Messiaen, Boellmann and Widor. The Recital will be followed by refreshments. No charge, donations in aid of church funds. </p>
          </div><!-- col-md-10 -->
